title: #92Noon! Live From Training Camp! Matt Birk/Daronte Jones
description: PA & Nordo are live from Vikings training camp at TCO Performance Center!  Matt Birk joins the show for the weekly Birk Bit. New Vikings DB Coach Daronte Jones chats with the guys about what it's been like working with the Vikings.
